ockquote><blockquote>同樓主既想法好相似 <br />\n成日都覺得自己一事無成 <br />\n同人一齊只會累左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，自己單機就算，唔想傷害其他人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔媾女同媾唔到係兩件事黎, 分清楚先</blockquote><br />\n兩樣野都可以一脈相承，媾唔到，衰得多，咪唔媾女囉。講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b53269b699135d0bf9090a67ea064d315fc04c","tid":276021,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T20:44:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7b0bc94312a06cdd037f4e026aa5635fdca8aff","tid":276021,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:07:41.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n返學應該識到唔少女同學<br />\n大膽啲<br />\n傾prj時咪私底下問下嘢<br />\n你性格正常嘅都應該冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開頭保持下距離<br />\n唔好下下秒覆人<br />\n會嚇親人<br />\n傾下傾下就做到朋友嫁啦<br />\n做到朋友睇下夾唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夾嘅有機會做到情侶嘅我諗<br />\n唔好怕柒<br />\n因為一定會有柒嘅一次<br />\n大膽啲<br />\n比啲信心比自己"},{"pid":"405e890fdb037d047974f11d28f50e55c0ac4900","tid":276021,"uid":77663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:29:26.000Z","msg":"不要再說鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360bf504db9382922565a53a0c7cdba30af1fd23","tid":276021,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:37:04.000Z","msg":"同我諗法好似 會對自己對另一半負責"},{"pid":"2c0ed9bb49d255cc8662716bb7830850e2cdd268","tid":276021,"uid":53836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"真係唔好害鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed024e6f5d75ecc168b0dd343dcbd4968f83458","tid":276021,"uid":58604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:21:41.000Z","msg":"同樓主諗法一樣<br />\n但我唔係媾唔到女<br />\n覺得比唔到將來佢地<br />\n但係其實女仔想要嘅唔係咩永遠呀將來呀<br />\n係